@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

participant "开发者" as Dev
participant "管理界面" as Dashboard
participant "线程池中间件" as Middleware
participant "业务应用A" as AppA
participant "业务应用B" as AppB

Dev -> Dashboard: 可视化操作
Dashboard -> Middleware: 发送管理指令
activate Middleware
Middleware -> AppA: 推送配置变更
activate AppA
AppA -> AppA: 动态更新线程池参数
AppA -> Middleware: 上报运行状态
deactivate AppA

Middleware -> AppB: 推送配置变更
activate AppB
AppB -> AppB: 动态更新线程池参数
AppB -> Middleware: 上报运行状态
deactivate AppB

Middleware -> Dashboard: 展示监控数据
deactivate Middleware
Dashboard -> Dev: 可视化展示

note right of Middleware
  **优点：**
  • 功能丰富完善
  • 可视化体验好
  • 扩展性强

  **缺点：**
  • 架构复杂度高
  • 运维成本增加
  • 稳定性依赖增多
end note

@enduml